<%= render "page_hero", title: "Store policy", subtitle: "Transparency you can trust." %>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row g-4">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3><i class="bi bi-shield-check me-2"></i>Privacy & data</h3>
        <p class="small mb-0">We collect only what’s needed to fulfill orders and improve your experience. We never sell your data. See our full Privacy Policy for details.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3><i class="bi bi-bag-check me-2"></i>Orders & cancellations</h3>
        <p class="small mb-0">Orders can be edited or cancelled within 1 hour of placement. Contact support with your order number.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3><i class="bi bi-emoji-smile me-2"></i>Quality guarantee</h3>
        <p class="small mb-0">If something isn’t right, we’ll make it right—refund, replace, or credit.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3><i class="bi bi-currency-dollar me-2"></i>Pricing & promos</h3>
        <p class="small mb-0">Promo codes must be applied at checkout and can’t be combined unless noted.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
